-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-sin-al-ithm","tag-arrogance-al-takabbur","tag-clothing-al-malabis","tag-extravagance","tag-food-al-taam","tag-manners-adab","tag-speech-al-qawl","tag-temperance-asceticism-zuhd","tag-al-ummah","tag-wealth-al-mal"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-96t","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":34999,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/19\/extravagant-food-clothing\/","url_meta":{"origin":34997,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Luxury: Worst Muslims extravagant in food, clothing, speech","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere will be men from my nation who eat a variety of foods, drink a variety of drinks, wear a variety of clothes, and are boastful in their speech. These are the worst of my nation.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13720,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/24\/barakah-enjoy-blessings-moderation\/","url_meta":{"origin":34997,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Blessings: Enjoy blessings of Allah in moderation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEat, drink, and give in charity. Wear nice clothing, but without pride or extravagance. Verily, Allah loves for His blessings to be seen upon His servants.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6708 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40111,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/14\/best-and-worst\/","url_meta":{"origin":34997,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: The best of you, the worst of you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best of you are those with the most excellent character and are careful of those around them. The worst of you are the pompous, the braggarts, and the pretentious.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 7621 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26310,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/05\/06\/umar-hawa-over-deen\/","url_meta":{"origin":34997,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Desires: Muslim destroyed if prefers desires over religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Mujahid reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cO people, beware of gluttony in eating. Verily, it causes laziness in prayer, it harms the body, it contracts disease, and Allah Almighty detests the fatness of a cleric. Rather, you must be moderate in your provisions, for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25977,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/26\/overeating-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34997,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Gluttony: Those who overate will be hungry in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the people who ate to their fill in the world today will be the people of hunger in the Hereafter tomorrow.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 11693 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Mundhiri \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14898,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/overeating-hungriest-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34997,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Gluttony: Those who overate will be hungriest in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the people who ate to their fill the most in this world will be the hungriest on the Day of Resurrection.\" Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3351 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuam